'''''D3RM3''''' was a [[Class-A cargo container]] in use by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Fleet]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].<ref name="XWCOSG">''[[X-Wing Collector's CD-ROM: The Official Strategy Guide]]''</ref>

During the [[evacuation of Yavin]], ''D3RM3'' was filled with a cache of [[Grain/Legends|grain]] and loaded aboard the Rebel [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] ''[[Op Mus]]''. When it broke down and was [[Mission to repair the Op Mus|ambushed]] in the [[Lesser Plooriod Cluster/Legends|Lesser Plooriod Cluster]], ''Op Mus'' was forced to dump the [[Cargo container/Legends|cargo container]] to flee the attack.<ref name="XWCOSG" />

While the Alliance sought new sources of food, it [[Mission to retrieve a grain supply|dispatched]] another [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]], ''[[Trips]]'', escorted by two [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing starfighters]], to secure the grain container for immediate use. [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]] and his wingmate succeeded in defeating several [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE fighters]] and the corvette ''[[Assassin 1]]'', protected ''Trips'' during the two minute transfer process, and escorted it back to the Alliance.<ref name="XWCOSG" />

